OL,3,CCoroner warns over viral trends after
OL,4,Cboy dies inhaling deodorant
OL,6,FIn May this year, Oliver and his
OL,7,Ffamily had returned home from a bank
OL,8,Fholiday weekend in Wales when the
OL,9,Fschoolboy said he was tired and went
OL,10,Fup to his bedroom, the coroner's
OL,11,Freport said.
OL,13,FWhen his mother called for him just
OL,14,Fbefore 6pm he did not respond.
OL,16,FShe found him unresponsive, called 999
OL,17,Fand carried out CPR until paramedics
OL,18,Farrived, the coroner said.
