OL,3,CCoroner warns over viral trends after
OL,4,Cboy dies inhaling deodorant
OL,6,FAn empty can fell from his bed when
OL,7,Fhis mother pulled the duvet back, and
OL,8,Fothers were later found in the room by
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FThe schoolboy's mother believed he was
OL,12,Fbeing bullied and raised her concerns
OL,13,Fwith staff just before the holiday,
OL,14,Fbut the school could not find any
OL,15,Fevidence, the report said.
OL,17,FThe coroner said the craze of inhaling
OL,18,Fdeodorant to "experience the buzz" is
OL,19,Fwidespread on social media, "including
OL,20,F` and particularly ` TikTok".
