OL,6,FMr Bridgman said: "It was not possible
OL,7,Fto access Oliver's mobile phone to
OL,8,Fdetermine whether Oliver had indulged
OL,9,Fin (the craze) directly from TikTok.
OL,11,F"The evidence was that it was,
OL,12,Fhowever, a challenge or practice known
OL,13,Fto be disseminated through TikTok."
OL,15,FThe coroner warned that "nothing
OL,16,Fappears to have changed" after a
OL,17,Frecent rise in such tragedies, adding
OL,18,Fthat future deaths will occur unless
OL,19,Faction is taken.
