OL,6,F"The posting of challenges ... on
OL,7,Fsocial media platforms will continue
OL,8,Fto take the lives of young,
OL,9,Fimpressionable and/or vulnerable
OL,10,Fchildren/teenagers unless the platform
OL,11,Fproviders take responsibility for
OL,12,Ftheir content and/or toxic algorithms
OL,13,Feither voluntarily or through
OL,14,FGovernment action," Mr Bridgman
OL,15,Fcontinued.
OL,17,F"The former seems unlikely."
